title: Renovated Apartment Homes - Amenity Rich - Maintenance Free Living !!!
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-Heated, Underground Garage Stalls Available with Convenient Car Washing Station', '-Pet Friendly Featuring Pet Spa and Bark Park', '-Stay Connected!', 'Wi-Fi in all Amenity Spaces', '-The Cyber Lounge Hosts a 24-hr, Self-Serve Coffee Bar, Pool Table and Computer Stations Making This a Great Place to Connect and Recharge', '-Controlled Access to Building Towers', '-Promenade Bike Trail and Bicycle Storage', '-The Cinema Offers Cozy Seating for Private Viewing Parties', '-Engineered wood plank flooring throughout', '-Host Out of Town Guests Overnight in the Guest Suite', '-The Playroom with Toys and Child-Friendly Computers', '-Over 20,000 Sq Ft of Amenities!', '-The Patio Offerings a Peaceful Outdoor Lounging Space, Accented with Four Gas Grills and a Gas Fire Pit', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
